description:
Are you up for a challenge? Do you like a dare? Walter Veith invites you to make a trial of Gods word. Why not believe what He says? Can the Bible be trusted? Are there things you dont understand? Professor Veith explains how to overcome doubt and shares how he handles passages that present seemingly unanswerable questions about evolution/creation, history, or anything else. Find out why, when put to the test, God has not disappointed him. Gods word can bear scrutiny and will stand the test. Are you ready to see how God will deal with the mountains of obstacles that stand between Him and you? Take the challenge.
